Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說 大家一起去溫泉旅行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起去溫泉旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那可是魅惑的清泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沐浴在溫暖與自然之中 讓暖流浸透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那經日勞頓為工作與戰鬥所累的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只要泡上一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就能萬病回春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,活血化瘀 舒筋活絡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,泡進遠離塵世喧囂的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,最能治癒你的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,景色也不錯 看上去挺舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我已經決定要睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣說死了真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,西部荒野的夢幻的神泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是有返老還童的功效呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明明只要泡一泡這溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就能年輕十歲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就能變回當年那個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,當年那個膚若凝脂的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,年輕 真好 年輕 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 明天一早在氣球起降場集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉 去讓亞文在今天內把氣球整備好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,琳卡也是 馬上開始打點行裝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,給我等著 夢幻的神泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要泡上一整個假期
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,出發了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,再喊一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 這樣大家就都去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒有和瑪麗恩她們一起出門旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,睡衣和毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,點心和牙刷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,258,121,,{\fs40.5}フラム
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,258,0,,{\fs27}火系炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,200,0,121,,{\fs40.5}クラフト
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,200,0,0,,{\fs27}物理系炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,0,56,,手雷和爆裂彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,138,121,,{\fs40.5}レヘルン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,138,0,,{\fs27}冰系炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,0,56,,冰球和…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,喂為什麼要這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 還需要這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,138,121,,{\fs40.5}オメガクラフト
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,138,0,,{\fs27}強化物理系炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,56,,終極爆裂彈！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,連這麼強力的東西都要帶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,以防萬一以防萬一啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好多行李啊 愛絲卡前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,妳都帶了些什麼啊 這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因為薇爾貝爾她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 大家都到齊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去好像很沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 未踏遺跡竟然離我們這麼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說柯爾賽特支部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了前往那座遺跡而設立的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然還沒人能去到那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 看得到山了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在冒煙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是火山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,能感覺到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的目的地就在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,終於快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,返老還童的神泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好多蒸汽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,神泉在哪裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在更深處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,神泉就在那座火山的山腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 向著山腳進發！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊那個不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那不過就是一般的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一般的溫泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,已經渾身是汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾 好想趕緊泡溫泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便哪兒都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一點點了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可不能因為妳還年輕就放棄喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡 我幫妳提包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 離火山這麼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩 找到溫泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,力量更強大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是這兒沒錯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,返老還童的神泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,總算到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是還不能泡進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,還有東西要調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才不幹 我可再等不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這一行千辛萬苦又平添了幾道皺紋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,現在就要撈回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,班長 您先請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我們先去那邊搭帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝了 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 先給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,來 來泡溫泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來 來 來 來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好滋潤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,疲憊的身體得以放鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了等等了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服 順便游個泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就一歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就兩歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就三歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,妳就這麼想返老還童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事想請教一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事啊 露希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做才能長得大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,長得大？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小後輩妳還真有眼光呢 找愛絲卡問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想問問愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做才能長得大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 怎麼妮歐妳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這還不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃飯好好運動就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,請妳們看看我一直做的運動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 腦子裡想著胸肌…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇 好麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要這麼費勁 還不如用魔法梆的一下變大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,梆的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然後讓我揉一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,妳手在往哪伸啊妮歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 沒忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 大家到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,妳問說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哇——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,難道不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是問身高啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,欸…欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,身高！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪個最先誤會的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是愛絲卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是愛絲卡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡前輩真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 露希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這不過是語言的多樣性…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 原來不是在說肌肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:59.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\move(189,408,21,408)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(200,0)\blur7.5\bord3\t(0,920,2,\blur0\bord0\1c&HFBDEF8&)}瑪麗恩•奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 亞文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你陪我們開發班出來旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我的夢想就是用自己的氣球飛向世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就當是在預演了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,世界的盡頭…就是那個古老傳說裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你還有這樣的夢想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不只是個普通的氣球機務哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 那個氣球到不了那麼遠的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,比如耗油量問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還有長距離航行需要的強度什麼的也不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 你蠻懂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉你也是憧憬藍天的一員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 倒不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這點想法 無論是誰都曾在腦海裡閃現過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是覺得不熟悉氣球的話是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒也說不上熟悉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 要是感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,隨時歡迎來維修班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉我們可是熱烈歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 不覺得從剛才開始變熱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說起來 好像確實溫度升高了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 好像氣泡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,果然出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪個吃了熊心豹子膽的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,膽敢擅闖奴家的聖地！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哇——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,從溫泉裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,渾身通紅的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,司火 力量最為強大的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直等著這一刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,與我締結契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,契約？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,契約是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,從前也跟姐姐一起去過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候是風之王就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是魔法師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有點事由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,想單刀直入跟妳締結契約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就算妳是魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,奴家可不聽人類使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哇——！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,果然情緒一如傳聞差得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,果然只能一戰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,輪到那些炸彈出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,給我等等 薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,難道妳的目的其實是跟這個精靈碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMS PGothic\b0\bord1.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7D4A2D&}(∀｀*ゞ)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMS PGothic\b0\bord1.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7D4A2D&}(∀｀*ゞ) {\r}你個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 大婆婆突然聯繫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾 最近沒向我報告修行的進展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,修行早就忘到九霄雲外去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒做啊怎麼辦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,確實聽說過火之王在這一帶以西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:17.64,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,88,,{\fs52.5}薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就像風之王那時候那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,乾淨俐落地簽個契約就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對哦 就這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人多少有點不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就把大家都叫上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好過分！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾 妳就這麼瞞著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還讓愛絲卡帶那麼多炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼不好嘛 幫我個忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你們那麼強…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,少廢話 少廢話 少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如今該奴家生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,奴家最討厭人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等… 請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼討厭人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,擅闖溫泉這件事 我們道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都從奴家的祭壇上搶去火焰了還有什麼好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,從祭壇？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,搶去火焰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是火之王說的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,被搶去火焰的祭壇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,破敗不堪都已經在崩塌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是盜掘遺跡的傢伙幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這個洞是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡曾經祭祀著精靈的寶玉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,精靈的寶玉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才火之王說的那個被搶去的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大概就是曾經人類為火之王而打造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,祭祀在此的寶玉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,聽大婆婆說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,過去有著這樣的習俗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說 人類給火之王的供品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,又被人類奪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,難怪她會討厭人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我來打造寶玉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:16:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想救贖火之王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,被曾經信賴的人類所背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,受了傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才會那麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 寶玉的做法咱們不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,打算怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我教妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,配方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然超難超難超級難的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就連老娘這樣的大魔法師也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 愛絲卡的話肯定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧 愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,放心等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就來做我們力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,琳卡和薇爾貝爾一起把石頭重新整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我 妮歐和露希爾來清掃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就直接去採集素材了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡請把其他材料準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是紫魂的水晶球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小心謹慎的話一定沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡 我們帶回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就備齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來就拜託了 愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,耐心等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對會救妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我們來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大家去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,難道都被火之王燒化了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看這招！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該進入終章了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,請看這晴空飛舞的火樹銀花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 真是漂亮的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,挺有能耐的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喔——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼覺得大家都很開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王的心情也不錯的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 你們三個 好可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,咱薇爾貝爾大人的魔法秀已經演完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想看的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,果不其然 不愧是愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,求求妳能行…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,奴家的聖域重新湧出火的力量了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 奴家的烈火熊熊燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡 原來是如此烈火燎原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因為失卻了那個寶玉 而失去了力量呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是火之王的聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,值得嘉獎 煉金術士小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你們和過往的人類不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有什麼困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,隨時歡迎你們來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,至此這件事就落下帷幕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,妳來這裡的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,喏 說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,火之王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,與我締結契約那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不締約也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,下次一個人來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以請等著我 直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,期待著卿與奴家刀刃相向的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好燙！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 總算能放鬆地泡溫泉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,修祭壇修得皮膚都乾巴巴的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就要撈回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 好像有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,呀——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼哥哥你們也在泡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我們還沒泡上啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,回去之前也想稍微泡一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 先說一聲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉你這大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼就砸我一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:34.14,Default,,0,0,12,,砰！夢想破滅了！
